  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting Language Rights in Kosovo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is to be viewed as a complementary initiative to the broader social inclusion programme with the overall objective to foster social inclusion through enhancing learning of official languages and enabling environment for equal use of official languages. To do so, the project will support the development of C1 curriculum for teaching Albanian/Serbian (as per the Common European Framework of Reference for Languages).</narrative>
  </description>
